data.description: HUNTINGTON PARK, 4+ BR, 3 Bath, over 2700sf in the Terry Sanford school district!  Located just minutes from the mall area, downtown & easy access to Ft Liberty.  You are welcomed by the huge landscaped yard, over half an acre in-town, with an inviting in-ground pool that has been professionally maintained.  The interior is well laid out for homeschooling, or home office, with a guest/in-law suite on the first floor!  Plenty of room for everyone.  The Great Room is accented by a brick wall & masonry fireplace.  The kitchen features stainless appliances, abundant cabinet space, and solid surface countertops.  Upstairs is a spacious owner's suite w/walk-in closet & bath with a double vanity.  An oversized 2-car garage has workspace/additional storage space.  Vacation at home!  The pool has an attractive wrought iron-looking fence around it, the entire backyard is privacy fenced. The interior & exterior have just been painted making this home ready for new owners!  Upgraded 2-10 Warranty included!
